text: Frank Ray Keyser (August 17, 1927 - March 7, 2015) was an American lawyer and politician from Vermont. He served as Speaker of the Vermont House of Representatives from 1959 to 1961, and 72nd Governor of Vermont from 1961 to 1963.National Governors Association , Biography, F.
